<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Digital Wave ICT Recruitment Portal</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

html{
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
background:#f5f7fb;
color:#222;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

header{
position:absolute;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
padding:20px 8%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
z-index:100;
}

.logo{
display:flex;
align-items:center;
gap:15px;
color:white;
font-weight:700;
font-size:24px;
}

.logo img{
width:60px;
height:60px;
border-radius:50%;
background:white;
padding:5px;
object-fit:contain;
}

.nav-btn{
background:#0d6efd;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
padding:14px 28px;
border-radius:50px;
font-weight:600;
transition:.3s;
}

.nav-btn:hover{
background:#0056d2;
}

.hero{
min-height:100vh;
background:
linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.75),rgba(0,0,0,.75)),
url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737604893-d14cc237f11d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.hero-content{
max-width:900px;
color:white;
}

.hero-badge{
display:inline-block;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);
padding:10px 18px;
border-radius:50px;
margin-bottom:20px;
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
}

.hero-content h1{
font-size:68px;
font-weight:800;
line-height:1.1;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero-content p{
font-size:20px;
line-height:1.8;
margin-bottom:35px;
opacity:.95;
}

.hero-buttons{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:15px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.primary-btn{
background:#0d6efd;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
padding:16px 35px;
border-radius:50px;
font-weight:600;
display:inline-block;
}

.secondary-btn{
background:white;
color:#0d6efd;
text-decoration:none;
padding:16px 35px;
border-radius:50px;
font-weight:600;
display:inline-block;
}

.success-box{
background:#d1fae5;
color:#065f46;
padding:16px;
max-width:800px;
margin:20px auto;
border-radius:12px;
text-align:center;
font-weight:600;
}

.container{
width:90%;
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
}

section{
padding:90px 0;
}

.section-title{
text-align:center;
font-size:42px;
color:#0d6efd;
margin-bottom:15px;
font-weight:700;
}

.section-subtitle{
text-align:center;
color:#666;
margin-bottom:50px;
}

.about{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:40px;
align-items:center;
}

.about-image img{
width:100%;
border-radius:25px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.about-content{
background:white;
padding:35px;
border-radius:25px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.about-content h3{
margin-bottom:15px;
color:#0d6efd;
}

.about-content p{
line-height:1.9;
color:#555;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.hero-content h1{
font-size:42px;
}

.hero-content p{
font-size:17px;
}

.about{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

header{
padding:15px;
}

.logo span{
font-size:18px;
}

}

</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">

<img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Digital Wave ICT">

<span>DIGITAL WAVE ICT</span>

</div>

<a href="#apply" class="nav-btn">
Apply Now
</a>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-content">

<div class="hero-badge">
Nationwide Recruitment • All Districts Welcome
</div>

<% if(success){ %>

<div class="success-box">
Application submitted successfully. Our recruitment team will review your application and contact you if shortlisted.
</div>

<% } %>

<h1>
Become A Digital Wave ICT Data Provider
</h1>

<p>
Join Malawi's growing network of Data Providers and help collect valuable information that supports businesses, research projects, development initiatives and digital transformation across all districts.
</p>

<div class="hero-buttons">

<a href="#apply" class="primary-btn">
Submit Application
</a>

<a href="#about" class="secondary-btn">
Learn More
</a>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="about">

<div class="container">

<h2 class="section-title">
About Digital Wave ICT
</h2>

<p class="section-subtitle">
Technology • Research • Innovation • Data Collection
</p>

<div class="about">

<div class="about-image">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80">

</div>

<div class="about-content">

<h3>
Who We Are
</h3>

<p>
Digital Wave ICT is a technology and information management company focused on research, data collection, digital services, business intelligence and community information systems. We are recruiting motivated individuals from every district in Malawi to join our Data Provider Program and contribute to building accurate and reliable information networks nationwide.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>
<style>

.stats{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
gap:20px;
margin-top:40px;
}

.stat-card{
background:white;
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
transition:.3s;
}

.stat-card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.stat-card h2{
font-size:40px;
color:#0d6efd;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.stat-card p{
color:#666;
font-weight:500;
}

.job-section{
background:#f8fbff;
}

.card-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
gap:25px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:35px;
border-radius:25px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.card h3{
color:#0d6efd;
margin-bottom:20px;
font-size:24px;
}

.card ul{
list-style:none;
}

.card ul li{
padding:10px 0;
color:#555;
border-bottom:1px solid #eee;
}

.card ul li:last-child{
border-bottom:none;
}

.benefits{
background:white;
}

.benefit-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:25px;
}

.benefit-card{
background:white;
padding:35px;
text-align:center;
border-radius:25px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
transition:.3s;
}

.benefit-card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.benefit-icon{
font-size:60px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.benefit-card h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#0d6efd;
}

.benefit-card p{
color:#666;
line-height:1.8;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.stats{
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
}

}

@media(max-width:600px){

.stats{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

}

</style>

<section>

<div class="container">

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>28</h2>
<p>Districts Covered</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>500+</h2>
<p>Active Data Providers</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>10K+</h2>
<p>Reports Collected</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>95%</h2>
<p>Data Accuracy Rate</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="job-section">

<div class="container">

<h2 class="section-title">
Available Position
</h2>

<p class="section-subtitle">
Data Provider Recruitment Program
</p>

<div class="card-grid">

<div class="card">

<h3>
Responsibilities
</h3>

<ul>

<li>✓ Collect community and district information</li>

<li>✓ Conduct surveys and field research</li>

<li>✓ Verify and validate collected data</li>

<li>✓ Submit reports through Digital Wave ICT systems</li>

<li>✓ Maintain professionalism and accuracy</li>

<li>✓ Work independently within assigned areas</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>
Requirements
</h3>

<ul>

<li>✓ Must be at least 18 years old</li>

<li>✓ Resident of selected district</li>

<li>✓ Must own or access a smartphone</li>

<li>✓ Basic internet knowledge</li>

<li>✓ Good communication skills</li>

<li>✓ Ability to meet reporting deadlines</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>
What We Offer
</h3>

<ul>

<li>✓ Flexible work opportunities</li>

<li>✓ Performance-based rewards</li>

<li>✓ Professional development</li>

<li>✓ Digital skills exposure</li>

<li>✓ Opportunity to work on national projects</li>

<li>✓ Long-term growth opportunities</li>

</ul>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="benefits">

<div class="container">

<h2 class="section-title">
Why Join Digital Wave ICT?
</h2>

<p class="section-subtitle">
Benefits of becoming a Data Provider
</p>

<div class="benefit-grid">

<div class="benefit-card">

<div class="benefit-icon">
💰
</div>

<h3>
Earn Opportunities
</h3>

<p>
Participate in projects and receive compensation based on approved assignments and performance.
</p>

</div>

<div class="benefit-card">

<div class="benefit-icon">
📱
</div>

<h3>
Work With Your Phone
</h3>

<p>
Most assignments can be completed using your smartphone and internet connection.
</p>

</div>

<div class="benefit-card">

<div class="benefit-icon">
🎓
</div>

<h3>
Build Experience
</h3>

<p>
Gain practical experience in data collection, research and digital information management.
</p>

</div>

<div class="benefit-card">

<div class="benefit-icon">
🌍
</div>

<h3>
Impact Communities
</h3>

<p>
Contribute valuable information that supports decision making and development projects.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>
<section id="apply" class="job-section">

<div class="container">

<h2 class="section-title">
Application Form
</h2>

<p class="section-subtitle">
Fill in your details to apply as a Digital Wave ICT Data Provider
</p>

<form action="/apply" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">

<div class="card-grid">

<div class="card">

<h3>Personal Information</h3>

<input type="text" name="fullName" placeholder="Full Name" required style="width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">

<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required style="width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">

<input type="number" name="age" placeholder="Age" required style="width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">

<select name="gender" required style="width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">
<option value="">Select Gender</option>
<option>Male</option>
<option>Female</option>
</select>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>Job Details</h3>

<select name="jobTitle" required style="width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">
<option>Data Provider</option>
<option>Field Officer</option>
<option>Survey Assistant</option>
<option>Research Assistant</option>
</select>

<select name="district" required style="width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">

<option value="">Select District</option>

<option>Balaka</option>
<option>Blantyre</option>
<option>Chikwawa</option>
<option>Chiradzulu</option>
<option>Dedza</option>
<option>Dowa</option>
<option>Karonga</option>
<option>Kasungu</option>
<option>Likoma</option>
<option>Lilongwe</option>
<option>Machinga</option>
<option>Mangochi</option>
<option>Mchinji</option>
<option>Mulanje</option>
<option>Mwanza</option>
<option>Mzimba</option>
<option>Neno</option>
<option>Nkhata Bay</option>
<option>Nkhotakota</option>
<option>Nsanje</option>
<option>Ntcheu</option>
<option>Ntchisi</option>
<option>Phalombe</option>
<option>Rumphi</option>
<option>Salima</option>
<option>Thyolo</option>
<option>Zomba</option>

</select>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>Upload Photo</h3>

<p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:10px;">
Upload a clear full-body photo (required)
</p>

<input type="file" name="photo" accept="image/*" required style="width:100%;padding:10px;margin:10px 0;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;">

<button type="submit" style="
width:100%;
padding:14px;
background:#0d6efd;
color:white;
border:none;
border-radius:12px;
font-weight:600;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:10px;
">
Submit Application </button>

</div>

</div>

</form>

</div>

</section>

<footer style="background:#111827;color:white;padding:50px 20px;text-align:center;margin-top:80px;">

<h2>Digital Wave ICT</h2>

<p style="margin-top:10px;color:#ccc;">
Building Malawi’s Digital Future Through Data & Innovation
</p>

<p style="margin-top:20px;color:#888;">
© 2026 Digital Wave ICT. All Rights Reserved.
</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
